---
title: Spicy Poblano Bolognese
description: We're amping up the classic Italian bolognese with one of our favorite ingredients - the poblano pepper. This faintly spicy Mexican pepper adds the perfect kick to a comforting pasta classic. Don't skimp on the parmesan!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54e491b66ced6e484a8b4569.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54e491b66ced6e484a8b4569.pdf
